1.00	Kris_Fisher	Kris Fisher	Francis "Kris" Fisher is a fictional character from the long-running Channel 4 soap opera Hollyoaks, played by Gerard McCarthy. The character first appeared on-screen in September 2006 and left in August 2010 after McCarthy quit the show. He is noted for his storylines involving the PEP drug, a bisexual love triangle, his outlandish personality and being the only permanent cross dressing character in a British soap opera. Following his departure, it was announced that McCarthy would return in November 2010 for a short stint.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/d/d3/Kris_Fisher.jpg/200px-Kris_Fisher.jpg
